OL,3,CRemembering Shildon Works 40 years
OL,4,Csince devastating closure
OL,6,FRachel Bullock spoke to former Shildon
OL,7,FWorks workers ahead of the 40th
OL,8,Fanniversary of its closure
OL,10,FForty years ago Shildon Wagon Works
OL,11,Fclosed - leaving the North East
OL,12,Fwithout one of its biggest and most
OL,13,Fimportant industrial giants.
OL,15,FThe town's wagon works sprang up just
OL,16,Fyears after the world's first
OL,17,Fpassenger train made its historic
OL,18,Fjourney through Shildon in 1825.
