OL,6,FIt made the horse and cart redundant,
OL,7,Fand the North East an industrial
OL,8,Fpioneer.
OL,10,FDr Thomas Spain, from the National
OL,11,FRailway Museum, said: "Anything from
OL,12,Fumbrella handles to jam jars would
OL,13,Fhave gone by rail and also raw
OL,14,Fmaterials for industry that fed into
OL,15,Fthe steelworks on Teesside, Port
OL,16,FTalbot in South Wales and everywhere
OL,17,Fin between.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
