OL,3,CRemembering Shildon Works 40 years
OL,4,Csince devastating closure
OL,6,F"She said, 'I can't believe it's
OL,7,Fhappening'. I could cry now."
OL,9,FAnother former worker added: "Work
OL,10,Fdoesn't just bring you money and wage,
OL,11,Fit also brings your pride and dignity.
OL,12,FAnd the same people who closed the
OL,13,Fworks were the very same ones who
OL,14,Fshortly after it shut were the ones
OL,15,Fattacking people from down here for
OL,16,Fbeing bone idle, lazy and unemployed.
OL,18,F"Shildon now has the cheapest housing
OL,19,Fin all of England. That's the legacy
OL,20,Fof the works closing."
